# Web app — Cursor rules

> Scoped to `apps/web/` and shared packages (`packages/core`, `packages/ui`).
> For repo-wide rules see root `AGENTS.md`. For full web app context see `apps/web/AGENTS.md`.

---

## Stack — always use these, no alternatives

- **React** (functional components + hooks only, no class components)
- **Tailwind CSS** (utility classes; shared preset from `packages/config`)
- **Norigin Spatial Navigation** for all focusable / D-pad interactive elements
- **Shaka Player** for all playback (`useShakaPlayer` hook in `apps/web/src/lib/shaka/`)
- **Zustand** for global state (small slices, no Redux)
- **Zod** for all data validation (in `packages/core`; infer types from schemas)
- **React Router v6** for routing
- **Lucide React** for icons (no second icon library)
- **Vitest** + **React Testing Library** + **MSW** for tests

---

## File structure — follow this exactly

```
apps/web/src/
  main.tsx          # SpatialNavigation.init() lives here
  App.tsx           # router shell only
  router.tsx
  pages/            # route-level components only
  features/         # self-contained feature folders (hooks + state + local components)
  lib/
    shaka/          # useShakaPlayer hook
    navigation/     # keybindings.ts + spatial nav config
    storage/        # localStorage storage adapter
  store/            # Zustand slices
```

---

## Rules

### Navigation
- Every interactive element **must** use `useFocusable` from Norigin.
- Every focusable region **must** have a stable, unique `focusKey` string constant.
- Use `isFocusBoundary: true` on container `FocusContext` nodes (Sidebar, ChannelList, EpgGrid, PlayerOverlay).
- Use `setFocus("KEY")` for programmatic focus changes on route transitions.
- All key bindings documented in `apps/web/src/lib/navigation/keybindings.ts`.

### Playback
- Only one `useShakaPlayer` instance at a time.
- Always call `destroy()` on unmount.
- Never autoplay speculatively — require an explicit user gesture.

### State
- One Zustand slice per domain: `sourcesStore`, `catalogStore`, `guideStore`, `profileStore`, `settingsStore`, `playerStore`.
- Persist only: `sourcesStore`, `profileStore`, `settingsStore` (via Zustand middleware).
- No direct `localStorage` calls outside the storage adapter in `lib/storage/`.

### CORS / source handling
- Always provide a "paste raw text" input alongside URL input.
- Surface CORS failures as `cors_blocked` error code — never as "invalid source."
- File import must always be supported.

### Shared packages
- `packages/core` — types, Zod schemas, parsers, storage adapter **interface** only. No React.
- `packages/ui` — shared React + Tailwind components. List `react`, `shaka-player`, and `@noriginmedia/norigin-spatial-navigation` as `peerDependencies`.
- Components must be headless-friendly: logic in hooks, styles in Tailwind classes.

### Code quality
- No `any` — use Zod-inferred types or explicit interfaces.
- No secrets or credentials in logs — diagnostics must be redacted.
- Co-locate tests: `*.test.ts` next to the file under test.
- Split components that exceed ~150 lines of JSX.
- Feature folders are self-contained: hooks, state, and local components stay together.

---

## Phase guard — do not build these yet

| Feature | Status |
| ------- | ------ |
| Xtream Codes UI | Deferred to Phase 4 — schema type exists, form UI does not |
| Full EPG grid | Phase 3 |
| Multiple profiles | Phase 4 |
| Cloud sync / accounts | Post-v1 |

When asked to build any of the above, flag it and confirm with the user before proceeding.

---

## Nx commands

```bash
nx affected --target=lint
nx affected --target=test
nx affected --target=build
nx g @nx/react:app apps/web
nx g @nx/js:lib packages/core
nx g @nx/react:lib packages/ui
```
